{"tid":924914,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"((選舉))邊首歌最適合做香港國歌?","createTime":"2018-12-02T12:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T08:14:15.000Z","uid":99568,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d42bd1f5e714cf8267da446f63d06784310c09b4","tid":924914,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"1號候選人<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RkcT0B-Vh8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRkcT0B-Vh8Y&d=rTRvicHDFQga4If2T3r4L%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2765831e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RkcT0B-Vh8Y</a><br />\n雖然呢首歌係特衰政府用嚟慶回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個人認為的而且確幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2號候選人<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FF0DowRJPfM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFF0DowRJPfM&d=rTRvicHDFQga4If2T3r4L%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f7b54706\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FF0DowRJPfM</a><br />\n呢首歌聽落去好感人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3號候選人<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qu_FSptjRic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqu_FSptjRic&d=rTRvicHDFQga4If2T3r4L%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1acad1c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qu_FSptjRic</a><br />\n呢首歌可以話係香港人經典中嘅經典, 不過佢唯一嘅唔好處就係成首歌冇句歌詞係有提及到同香港有關嘅嘢同埋呢首歌支那人都好鍾意唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4號候選人<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ah1DC_dn8ws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fah1DC_dn8ws&d=rTRvicHDFQga4If2T3r4L%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e699de8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ah1DC_dn8ws</a><br />\n國父陳雲bb豬<br />\n就係呢個理由已經值得佢成為香港國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5號候選人<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ca9vsEkKrL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fca9vsEkKrL4&d=rTRvicHDFQga4If2T3r4L%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e8f24ffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ca9vsEkKrL4</a><br />\n呢首歌應該係大熱 講述獅子山下香港人不屈不撓拼搏嘅熱血生活態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家請投票<br />\n請打((1))如果 你想投((1))<br />\n如此類推<br />\n<br />\n投票完之後麻煩講下點解你會頭呢位候選人<br />\n<br />\n到咗1001之後我就會開始點票<br />\n點票完成之後我就會正式宣佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abef64bcc8b5aba1c6cc289c2d23c03f88d991e1","tid":924914,"uid":175683,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾Post都想到1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387de4a89b5facc354f4bee6aaf8b7185a106009","tid":924914,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"((2))小弟先投為敬<br />\n我投二號嘅原因係因為 呢首歌最好聽 歌詞入面最有意義"},{"pid":"11f651c6b823897a72b860d4ef85c46848182026","tid":924914,"uid":221265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d42bd1f5e714cf8267da446f63d06784310c09b4","tid":924914,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"1號候選人<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RkcT0B-Vh8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRkcT0B-Vh8Y&d=rTRvicHDFQga4If2T3r4L%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2765831e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RkcT0B-Vh8Y</a><br />\n雖然呢首歌係特衰政府用嚟慶回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個人認為的而且確幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" clas